Fony nivoaka avy tany Egypta ny Isiraely , Dia ny taranak' i Jakoba avy tany amin' ny firenena hafa fiteny , ||| When Israel left Egypt , when the family of Jacob left a foreign nation behind ,
Joda no fitoerany masina , Isiraely no fanjakany . ||| Judah became his sanctuary , Israel his kingdom .
Ny ranomasina nahita ka nandositra ; Ary niorika Jordana . ||| The sea looked and fled ; the Jordan River turned back .
Ny tendrombohitra dia nifalihavanja tahaka ny ondrilahy , Ary ny havoana tahaka ny zanak' ondry . ||| The mountains skipped like rams , the hills like lambs .
Inona izato mahazo anao , ry ranomasina , no mandositra ianao ? Ary ianao , ry Jordana , no miorika ianao ? ||| Why do you flee , O sea ? Why do you turn back , O Jordan River ?
Ary ianareo tendrombohitra , no mifalihavanja tahaka ny ondrilahy ; Ary ianareo havoana , tahaka ny zanak' ondry ? ||| Why do you skip like rams , O mountains , like lambs , O hills ?
Mihorohoroa eo anatrehan' ny Tompo , ry tany , Dia eo anatrehan' Andriamanitr' i Jakoba . ||| Tremble , O earth , before the Lord - before the God of Jacob ,
Izay mampody ny vatolampy ho rano monina Ary ny afovato ho loharano . ||| who turned a rock into a pool of water , a hard rock into springs of water !
